OL,3,CDrink-drive footballer says he'll take
OL,4,Ca bus to training after driving ban
OL,6,FWhen his lawyer asked him how he would
OL,7,Freact to losing his driving licence,
OL,8,Fknowing how footballers are often
OL,9,Fwedded to their cars and driving, he
OL,10,Ftold him a driving ban is "the least
OL,11,Fof my worries. I will get a bus to
OL,12,Ftraining".
OL,14,FThe court heard that police received a
OL,15,F999 call from a witness reporting a
OL,16,FNissan Juke swerving and being driven
OL,17,Ferratically.
