OL,3,CDrink-drive footballer says he'll take
OL,4,Ca bus to training after driving ban
OL,6,FPolice traced the number plate and
OL,7,Fwent to Ilmari Niskanen's home. A
OL,8,Fbreath test revealed he had 70
OL,9,Fmicrograms of alcohol per 100ml or
OL,10,Fbreath, which is twice the limit.
OL,12,FNiskanen gave a full and frank
OL,13,Fadmission and expressed remorse.
OL,15,FThe court heard that the public
OL,16,Fstatement which had been released by
OL,17,Fthe club was prompted by his desire to
OL,18,Fbe honest about what had happened,
OL,19,Fearlier rather than later.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
