OL,3,CDrink-drive footballer says he'll take
OL,4,Ca bus to training after driving ban
OL,6,FThe court was told he has suffered
OL,7,Fsignificant embarrassment,
OL,8,Fparticularly due to the media coverage
OL,9,Fback home in Finland, where he is a
OL,10,Fmember of the national team and he has
OL,11,Fbeen concerned about the consequences
OL,12,Ffor his international career.
OL,14,FHis lawyer told the court he has said
OL,15,F"It is the worst thing I have ever
OL,16,Fdone"
