OL,3,CDrink-drive footballer says he'll take
OL,4,Ca bus to training after driving ban
OL,6,FNiskanen appeared before a District
OL,7,FJudge who said: "I am sure you are
OL,8,Fdisappointed to be in this position"
OL,9,Fbut "you can consider yourself
OL,10,Fextremely fortunate", due to the
OL,11,Fpossibility that there could have been
OL,12,Fan accident.
OL,14,FHe told him: "Thankfully in your case
OL,15,Fthere wasn't. It could have been a
OL,16,Fgreat deal worse than it is".
OL,18,FNiskanen was given credit for his
OL,19,Fcooperation at every stage of the
OL,20,Fprocess and the judge said he believed
OL,21,Fhe had shown genuine remorse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
