OL,4,Ca bus to training after driving ban
OL,6,FThe initial fine was set at #3,000, it
OL,7,Fwas reduced to #2,000 as credit for
OL,8,Fthe guilty plea. He has to pay costs
OL,9,Fand victim surcharge amounting to #885.
OL,11,FHe was disqualified from driving for
OL,12,F18 months. This can be reduced by 25%
OL,13,Fif he completed a training course.JThe
OL,14,Fjudge finished by saying "I don't
OL,15,Fthink we will see you again - lesson
OL,16,Flearned!"
